                    <p>
                        Feel free to contact us on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/school.danlab" class="underline font-semibold hover:text-pink-500 transition duration-200">Facebook</a>, <a href="https://www.instagram.com/danlab_school/?fbclid=IwAR07uTjdcEvWoFG-3DN3j3cNSf4wJZLlY91hbPtL7sDbVdJ8S_cUYWWUlfc" class="underline font-semibold hover:text-pink-500 transition duration-200">Instagram</a>, <a href="https://t.me/danlabschool" class="underline font-semibold hover:text-pink-500 transition duration-200">Telegram</a> or <a href="mailto:contact@danlabschool.com" class="underline font-semibold hover:text-pink-500 transition duration-200">e-mail</a>!!
                    </p>
                    <p>See you! 👋🏼</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
